quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  27,45,"GooŇč…óii Min Nulii fa'ade e Samuudinkoo…ďe …ďen musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on Saalihu, …óum woni rewee Alla. Tawi kam…ďe ko …ďe feddeeji …ói…ói hi…ďe bee√Īondira."
  27,46,"O maaki: "Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, ko fii hol…óum he√Īornton bone …óen ko adii mo∆ī∆īere nden?" "Ko ha…ói imsinanao Alla mbelejo'o onon on njurminoyte"."
  27,47,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Min kiitinorii ma e …ďen won'…óu…ďe e maa…óa". O maaki: "kiite moo…óon on ko ka Alla woni, ko woni, onon ko on yim…ďe fitnetee…ďe""
  27,48,"Laatinoke ka saare ton wor…ďe njeenayo he…ďe mbonna ka leydi …ďe mo∆ī∆īintaa."
  27,49,"∆Āe mb'i: ∆Āe ngoo…óndirii Alla, ma min waalanan mo ka suudu kaŇčko e …ďeynguure makko nden refti ma min wi'an jey…ďe mo …ďen; men tawaaka bargol yim…ďe makko …ďen, e pellet, menen ko men gooŇč…óu…ďe"."
  27,50,"∆Āe kodi hodoore Minen kadi Min pewji fewjoore, tawi kam…ďe …ďe so'ataa."
  27,51,"Ndaaru, ko honno laatorno battane hodo ma…ď…ďe ngon, Minen Min njirbinno …ďe kam…ďe e yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen …ďe fof ma…ď…ďe."
  27,52,"∆äin cuu…ói ma…ď…ďe ko jeewu…ói sabu ko …ďe too√Īunoo kon. Pellet, wonii e …óum Ma'ande wonan'de yim…ďe haqqiloo…ďe …ďen."
  27,53,"Min danndi …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe, …ďe ngoni huloo…ďe [Alla]."
  27,54,"E Luutu, tuma nde o wi'anno yim…ďe makko …ďen: 'Enee, on aray paŇčkare …óen hara ho…óon cutii?""
  27,55,"Eyoo, onon on ngarat e wor…ďe …ďen ka tuuyo ngccon rew…ďe …ďen?! Si ko woni, onon ko on yim…ďe majjaa…ďe."